<section id="about-us" class="about-us">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <div class="story-section">
      <h3>A Blend of Experience and Passion</h3>
      <p>
        Welcome to The Speechsmiths' Forge, where over three decades of teaching
        English, two decades of coaching presentations, and a lifetime in the
        theater converge to create a unique, empathetic approach to presentation
        coaching. Our founder's journey through theater, teaching, and running
        small businesses, combined with specialized training in startups, has
        shaped a service that's more than just coaching – it's a transformative
        experience.
      </p>
      <div class="illustration-placeholder">Illustration Here</div>
    </div>
    <div class="story-section">
      <h3>Our Philosophy: Empathy, Creativity, Humanity</h3>
      <p>
        At the heart of our coaching is a belief in the power of empathy,
        creativity, and humanity. We understand that you know your product and
        yourself better than anyone else. Our role is not to teach you how to
        give a presentation, but to guide you in amplifying your strengths and
        minimizing weaknesses. It's about building confidence and effectiveness
        in your communication, tailored to who you are and what you do.
      </p>
      <div class="illustration-placeholder">Illustration Here</div>
    </div>
    <div class="story-section">
      <h3>Our Services</h3>
      <p>
        We offer a range of services designed to cater to various presentation
        needs – whether you're a seasoned professional seeking to hone your
        skills or a startup entrepreneur preparing for your first big pitch. Our
        services include individual presentation coaching, group workshops on
        public speaking, virtual presentation skills training, and more. We are
        also constantly evolving, adding new offerings to meet the diverse needs
        of our clients.
      </p>
      <div class="illustration-placeholder">Illustration Here</div>
    </div>
    <div class="story-section">
      <h3>Empowering Success</h3>
      <p>
        Our mission is simple: to see more success in the world. We believe that
        effective communication is a key to success, and we're here to help
        unlock that potential in you.
      </p>
      <div class="illustration-placeholder">Illustration Here</div>
    </div>
    <div class="story-section">
      <h3>Special Focus on International Clients</h3>
      <p>
        We have a special place in our hearts for international clients,
        particularly those for whom English is a second language. Our expertise
        is especially beneficial for Korean business professionals and startups,
        offering them the tools and confidence needed to succeed in the global
        market.
      </p>
      <div class="illustration-placeholder">Illustration Here</div>
    </div>
    <div class="story-section">
      <h3>Looking Ahead</h3>
      <p>
        As we continue to grow and evolve, we're excited about the future. Our
        vision is to expand our reach, develop new, innovative coaching methods,
        and continue empowering individuals and businesses with the art of
        effective presentation.
      </p>
      <div class="illustration-placeholder">Illustration Here</div>
    </div>
    <div class="story-section">
      <h3>Join Us on This Journey</h3>
      <p>
        We invite you to explore what we have to offer and see how we can be a
        part of your success story. Whether you're looking to improve your
        presentation skills, gain confidence in public speaking, or simply learn
        how to communicate more effectively, we're here to help.
      </p>
      <div class="illustration-placeholder">Illustration Here</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="call-to-action">
    <a href="#contact" class="cta-button">Join Our Journey</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #about-us {
    background: url("parchment-bg.png") no-repeat center center;
    background-size: cover;
    padding: 50px 0;
    color: #333; /* A dark color for contrast */
  }

  .about-us .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 15px;
  }

  .about-us h2 {
    color: #7b2d26; /* A color that stands out against the parchment */
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .about-us h3 {
    color: #7b2d26; /* Same as the main heading for consistency */
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .about-us p {
    background-color: rgba(
      255,
      255,
      255,
      0.8
    ); /* Slightly transparent white for readability */
    padding: 15px;
    border-left: 5px solid #7b2d26; /* Adds a touch of design without being overwhelming */
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* Storytelling Animation */
  .story-section {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(50px);
    visibility: hidden;
    transition:
      opacity 0.6s ease-out,
      transform 0.6s ease-out,
      visibility 0.6s;
  }

  .story-section.active {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
    visibility: visible;
  }

  /* Placeholder for Illustration */
  .illustration-placeholder {
    height: 150px; /* Set desired height */
    background-color: #eaeaea; /* Placeholder color */
    margin: 20px 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    font-style: italic;
    /* Add more styles as needed */
  }

  /* Call to Action */
  .call-to-action {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 50px;
  }

  .cta-button {
    background-color: red; /* Adjust to match your color scheme */
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background-color: darkred; /* Darker shade for effect */
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  /* Responsive Typography */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-us h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .about-us h3 {
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .about-us p {
      font-size: 16px;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  window.addEventListener("scroll", revealSections);

  function revealSections() {
    var sections = document.querySelectorAll(".story-section");

    for (var i = 0; i < sections.length; i++) {
      var windowHeight = window.innerHeight;
      var elementTop = sections[i].getBoundingClientRect().top;
      var elementVisible = 7; // Amount of the element that must be visible

      if (elementTop < windowHeight - elementVisible) {
        sections[i].classList.add("active");
      } else {
        sections[i].classList.remove("active");
      }
    }
  }

  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", revealSections);
</script>
